text: Rafik Sorman () is a Libyan football club based in Sorman, Libya. The team played in Libyan Premier League in 2007, but were relegated at the end of the season. ==Current players== :* Abdulwahab Hassn :* Rabe Al Msellati Category:Football clubs in Libya Category:Association football clubs established in 1959 Category:Sorman Category:1959 establishments in Libya
